$primary-gradient: linear-gradient(180deg, #BC9CFF 0%, #8BA4F9 100%)
$primary-color: #BC9CFF
$secondary-gradient: linear-gradient(180deg, #6FCF97 0%, #66D2EA 100%)

// Colors
$dark-100: rgba(31, 32, 65, 1)
$dark-75: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.75)
$dark-50:rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.5)
$dark-25: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.25)
$dark-5: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.05)
$purple: #BC9CFF
$green: #6FCF97
.login-button
  display: flex
  align-items: center
  height: 34px
  margin-right: 20px
  background: #fff
  color: $primary-color
  position: relative
  box-sizing: border-box
  border: 2px solid transparent
  background-clip: padding-box

.login-button::before
  content: ""
  position: absolute
  margin: -2px
  top: 0px
  bottom: 0px
  left: 0px
  right: 0px
  background: $primary-gradient
  border-radius: inherit
  z-index: -1

@import '../sass/variables'
@import '../fonts/fonts'

// Header styles
@import '../blocks/page/page'
@import '../blocks/header/header'
@import '../blocks/container/container'
@import '../blocks/header/__container/header__container'
@import '../blocks/logo/_logo'
@import '../blocks/menu/menu'
@import '../blocks/menu/__list/menu__list'
@import '../blocks/menu/__item/menu__item'
@import '../blocks/menu/__link/menu__link'
@import '../blocks/dropdown/dropdown'
@import '../blocks/dropdown/__content/dropdown__content'
@import '../blocks/dropdown/__link/dropdown__link'
@import '../blocks/button/_button'
@import '../blocks/header/__button/header__button'
@import '../blocks/login-button/login-button'
@import '../blocks/register-button/register-button'

section
  padding: 50px

.color
  width: 50px
  height: 50px

// Colors

.color:nth-of-type(1)
  background-color: $dark-100

.color:nth-of-type(2)
  background-color: $dark-75

.color:nth-of-type(3)
  background-color: $dark-50

.color:nth-of-type(4)
  background-color: $dark-25

.color:nth-of-type(5)
  background-color: $dark-5

.color:nth-of-type(6)
  background-color: $purple

.color:nth-of-type(7)
  background-color: $green

// Texts

.title
  font-family: 'Montserrat'
  font-style: normal
  font-weight: bold
  font-size: 24px
  line-height: 29px
  color: $dark-100

.section__title
  font-family: 'Montserrat'
  font-style: normal
  font-weight: bold
  font-size: 19px
  line-height: 23px
  color: $dark-100

.label__text
  font-family: 'Montserrat'
  font-style: normal
  font-weight: bold
  font-size: 12px
  line-height: 15px
  text-transform: uppercase
  color: $dark-100

.text
  font-family: 'Montserrat'
  font-style: normal
  font-weight: normal
  font-size: 14px
  line-height: 24px
  color: $dark-75

// Form elements

.form-elements
  display: flex
  flex-direction: column
  align-items: flex-start

.form__item
  display: flex
  flex-direction: column
  align-items: flex-start
  margin-bottom: 20px
  position: relative

.form__group
  display: flex
  flex-direction: row

.form__group .form__item
  margin-right: 20px

.form__group_type_checkbox .text
  margin-bottom: 10px

.form__group_type_radio .text
  margin: 0 20px 0 10px

.form__input
  height: 44px
  width: 320px
  margin: 0
  padding: 13px 15px
  border: 0
  box-sizing: border-box
  border: 1px solid $dark-25
  border-radius: 4px
  font-family: 'Montserrat'
  font-weight: normal
  font-size: 14px
  line-height: 18px
  color: $dark-75
  position: relative

.form__input::-webkit-input-placeholder 
  color: $dark-25
        
.form__input::-moz-placeholder 
  color: $dark-25
        
.form__input:-ms-input-placeholder 
  color: $dark-25
        
.form__input:-moz-placeholder
  color: $dark-25

.form__input:hover,
.form__input:focus
  border: 1px solid $dark-75
  box-sizing: border-box
  border-radius: 4px
  outline: 0

.form__label
  margin-bottom: 5px

.dropdown:after
  display: flex
  justify-content: center
  align-items: center
  content: '>',
  position: absolute
  top: 0
  right: 0
  width: 44px
  height: 44px

.dropdown_type_date
  width: 150px

.dropdown_type_filter-date
  width: 267px

.form__input:disabled
  background-color: transparent

.form__submit-button
  width: 267px
  display: flex
  justify-content: center
  align-items: center
  position: absolute
  bottom: 0
  right: 0
  width: 44px
  height: 44px
  background: transparent
  border: 0

.form__checkbox
  width: 20px
  height: 20px
  margin: 2px 10px 0 0

.form__checkbox + .text
  max-width: 200px

.form__radio
  margin: auto 0
  width: 20px
  height: 20px

.button
  outline: 0
  border: 0
  padding: 15px 20px
  margin: 0
  font-family: 'Montserrat'
  text-transform: uppercase
  font-weight: bold
  background: $primary-gradient
  height: 44px
  border-radius: 22px
  color: #fff


.button_type_white
  display: flex
  align-items: center
  background: $primary-gradient
  -webkit-background-clip: text
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent
  position: relative
  box-sizing: border-box
  border: 2px solid transparent
  background-clip: padding-box
  z-index: 1

.button_type_white::before
  content: ""
  position: absolute
  margin: -2px
  top: 0px
  bottom: 0px
  left: 0px
  right: 0px
  background: $primary-gradient
  border-radius: inherit
  z-index: -1

.button_type_white::after
  content: ''
  background: #fff
  position: absolute
  top: 0
  left: 0
  bottom: 0
  right: 0
  z-index: -1
  border-radius: inherit

.button_type_transparent
  background: $primary-gradient
  -webkit-background-clip: text
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent

.form__cost-range
  margin: 0 0 0 auto

.form__input_type_range
  -webkit-appearance: none
  width: 100%
  background: transparent

.form__input_type_range::-webkit-slider-thumb 
  -webkit-appearance: none
  width: 12px
  height: 12px
  background: $secondary-gradient
  border: 2px solid #FFFFFF
  border-radius: 10px
